                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-518-18800913 t18800913-518-punishment-43"></join>Five Years' Penal Servitude.</rs>
                  </hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">ELIZABETH MONTAGUE</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18800913-518-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
